                <p>By participating in the contest, members agree to be bound by these rules and to all decisions of TopCoder, which are final, binding and conclusive in all matters.</p>
                <p><span class="bigRed">Contestants must not cheat. All submissions must be the contestant's alone and must not have been written by anyone other than the contestant.</span></p>
                <p>Winners will be notified via email within ten (10) days of the completion of the member voting that they have won a prize.</p>
